## HolyClaude (inspiration)

- License: MIT
- Copyright: 2026 CoderLuii
- Source: https://github.com/CoderLuii/HolyClaude

KroClaude reuses the HolyClaude project's structural approach (Dockerfile
layout, s6-overlay supervisor pattern, Apprise notification helper, and
documentation/configuration patterns) under the terms of HolyClaude's MIT
license. KroClaude does not redistribute the HolyClaude source code; it
re-implements the in-scope subset (per
`specs/001-claude-shell-base/spec.md`) with deliberate divergences:

- The `@siteboon/claude-code-ui` ("CloudCLI") web UI and its plugins are
  NOT bundled in KroClaude. The CloudCLI patches HolyClaude applies to
  that bundle are correspondingly absent here.
- Several optional CLIs and packages (Cursor, Junie, OpenCode, Azure CLI,
  Wrangler, Vercel, Netlify CLI, PM2, Prisma, Drizzle, etc.) are not
  installed.
- The slim/full profile system is removed.
- The runtime UID/GID remap (`PUID`/`PGID`) is removed; KroClaude uses
  named Docker volumes only.

